== Video with omxplayer ==
<pre># omxplayer -o local <filename></pre>
^ head phones output

<pre># omxplayer -o hdmi <filename></pre>
^ hdmi output

<pre># omxplayer -r <filename></pre>
^ full screen, skewed though?

<pre># setterm -blank force && omxplayer filename
# setterm -blank poke</pre>
^ command on console so only the video shows (and not console text scroll back), poke gets it back

